{"prompt": "Create a digital hub for a local craft brewery. The branding should include a distinctive amber yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Local Brews Hub</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8e7a1;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #e6b800;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #b38f00 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2, h3 {\n            color: #e6b800;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .brew-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .brew-item {\n            background-color: #fffbe6;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #e6b800;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .brew-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .brew-item h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #e6b800;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background: #e6b800;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-top: #b38f00 2px solid;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #333;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Local Brews Hub</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#beers\">Our Beers</a>\n            <a href=\"#visit\">Visit Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"main-content\">\n            <article>\n                <h2 id=\"about\">About Us</h2>\n                <p>Welcome to the digital home of your favorite local craft brewery! We're passionate about brewing exceptional beers with the finest ingredients and a whole lot of heart. From crisp lagers to bold IPAs, we have something for every palate. Come experience the difference that local dedication makes.</p>\n            </article>\n            <hr>\n            <article>\n                <h2 id=\"beers\">Our Latest Brews</h2>\n                <div class=\"brew-list\">\n                    <div class=\"brew-item\">\n                        <h4>Golden Ale</h4>\n                        <p>A smooth, easy-drinking ale with a hint of citrus. Perfect for any occasion.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"brew-item\">\n                        <h4>Amber Lager</h4>\n                        <p>A classic amber lager with a rich malt backbone and a clean finish.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"brew-item\">\n                        <h4>IPA Revolution</h4>\n                        <p>An aggressively hopped IPA bursting with tropical fruit and pine notes.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"brew-item\">\n                        <h4>Stout Night</h4>\n                        <p>A dark, decadent stout with notes of coffee and dark chocolate.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <hr>\n            <article>\n                <h2 id=\"visit\">Visit Us</h2>\n                <p>Join us at our taproom for a taste of the freshest brews. We offer flights, pints, and growler fills!</p>\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Brewery Lane, Craftville, CA 90210</p>\n                <p><strong>Hours:</strong></p>\n                <p>Mon-Thurs: 3 PM - 9 PM</p>\n                <p>Fri-Sat: 12 PM - 10 PM</p>\n                <p>Sunday: 12 PM - 8 PM</p>\n            </article>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Local Brews Hub. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}